            <h4>How to get there</h4>
            <p>From Manila, IGACOS is an hour and a half flight bound to Davao City, the gateway to the Island City. The jump off point to Samal is a 7-minute taxi ride from the Davao International Airport to Km-11, Sasa, located behind the Sasa Public Market IGACOS is just about 10-minutes across the Pakiputan Strait.</p>
            <p>By RORO or launches, one may board the ferryboard with or without your vehicle. One may also opt to take the passenger launches at Km-11 for only 10 minutes.</p>
